1. *Ostane* mu mnogo vremena da se odmori (He will have a lot of time to rest).
2. Učenje je mučno, ali *ostane* nam još mnogo da naučimo (Learning is hard, but we still have a lot to learn).
3. Ona će uvek da *ostane* u našim mislima (She will always stay in our thoughts).
4. Moraću da *ostanem* kod kuće (I will have to stay at home).
5. *Ostalo* je još mnogo da se uradi (There is still a lot to be done).
6. On je rekao da će *ostati* u gradu (He said he will stay in the city).
7. Ona je rekla da će *ostati* u školi (She said she will stay in school).